{"tid":808572,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急 !!]  飲咖啡飲到個腦會沉一沉，慢慢谷5秒，再爆炸，好撚驚！！","createTime":"2018-09-06T12:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T09:35:37.000Z","uid":123335,"like":207,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"3b373ea95be7f78c5a6bd7b55f3a10de8c66a257","tid":808572,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n好撚驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來唔知咩事 <br />\n<br />\n話就我今日早餐後飲左杯濃咖啡 <br />\n初初都冇咩事<br />\n<br />\n但我午餐後（約30 分鐘）<br />\n又再飲多杯濃咖啡<br />\n<br />\n點知隔左個幾鐘 <br />\n個腦突然沉一沉，然後睇野會慢晒，世界變左慢鏡<br />\n然後個腦會慢慢谷，谷左5秒左右，<br />\n然後會有種「谷爆腦」既感覺 .... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會感到少量嘔心，頭部不適 .... <br />\n<br />\n之後再隔2個鐘，放工啦 <br />\n屌，個腦又突然沉一沉，Loop 多次「爆腦」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我落街跑步<br />\n跑左30分鐘，<br />\n屌，個腦又突然沉一沉，Loop 多次「爆腦」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n點解會咁架<br />\n<br />\n好撚恐佈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢個情況之前我都試過好多次，總之我一（餐後30 mins ）飲濃咖啡<br />\n就會咁<br />\n有冇醫學／科學JJ 知我身體發生左咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有酒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141138f2441d73de2115cfe31b59369b675dba17","tid":808572,"uid":89931,"like":501,"dislike":2,"score":499,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"你應該直接右轉去睇醫生 唔係上嚟問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d2d0e4fc7b9eb8dc4d2fd61b72d3ff35fa09eb","tid"