浮下浮下咁<br />\n<br />\n我諗我地係唔岩飲咖啡, 我之前無飲一路都無事, 係琴日太無精神就試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"咖啡因係咁"},{"pid":"8755a270cd635861bd6663f6a654e3896f60e151","tid":808572,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"血管？"},{"pid":"29687c580895699ce30dca520786df836f6b071f","tid":808572,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff7b0e7ada1230218697778b4d0ad3ee4ebf52a","tid":808572,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"之前試過咖啡中毒<br />\n<br />\n每日定唔知係短時間內飲既咖啡因份量唔可以多過400mg<br />\n如果唔係就好似我試過既 暈 想嘔 無力 等症狀<br />\n<br />\n當時醫生係幫我洗胃<br />\n<br />\n如果去唔到醫院 可以選擇即刻飲大量既水<br />\n<br />\n但其實呢d係急性症狀 樓主呢d應該同咖啡冇關"},{"pid":"29c641498ccba030d342f5a195d0872dd0ddf490","tid":808572,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"潮文？"},{"pid":"92ff1eeafd43cec1c68cf0ff0702efacc8c9161d","tid":808572,"uid":179855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3b373ea95be7f78c5a6bd7b55f3a10de8c66a257","tid":808572,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n好撚驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來唔知咩事 <br />\n<br />\n話就我今日早餐後飲左杯濃咖啡 <br />\n初初都冇咩事<br />\n<br />\n但我午餐後（約30 分鐘）<br />\n又再飲多杯濃咖啡<br />\n<br />\n點知隔左個幾鐘 <br />\n個腦突然沉一沉，然後睇野會慢晒，世界變左慢鏡<br />\n然後個腦會慢慢谷，谷左5秒左右，<br />\n然後會有種「谷爆腦」既感覺 .... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會感到少量嘔心，頭部不適 .... <br />\n<br />\n之後再隔2個鐘，放工啦 <br />\n屌，個腦又突然沉一沉，Loop 多次「爆腦」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我落街跑步<br />\n跑左30分鐘，<br />\n屌，個腦又突然沉一沉，Loop 多次「爆腦」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n點解會咁架<br />\n<br />\n好撚恐佈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢個情況之前我都試過好多次，總之我一（餐後30 mins ）飲濃咖啡<br />\n就會咁<br />\n有冇醫學／科學JJ 知我身體發生左咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有酒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"就快變新人類，我以前都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28efc5ce0b982ca706b461ecef9930936b385b98","tid":808572,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"上年年尾空肚飲咗兩杯濃縮咖啡，之後坐船入長洲，撞正全年最熱嗰日，曬到半暈半醒即刻入咗間鋪一口氣食咗兩個餐，回程差啲暈係架船 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a674a797702a94d98feab13f0c084a96af6c3a63","tid":808572,"uid":46200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"似係血管收縮<br />\n血液唔上腦<br />\n但突然又通番<br />\n血湧曬上去<br />\n就有咁嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n盡快睇醫生<br />\n唔係好易中風"},{"pid":"051b84b686f28dec0b4bdbc1c1d99567e0801f1d","tid":808572,"uid":201761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"超能力？"},{"pid":"1af618a15787815eec48340dfc111a916fa6bf14","tid":808572,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"樓主應該開發咗自己潛能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6541dc4abbdd72660e2b754ef705b25e880449","tid":808572,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68c16b17854f55f9d04e5adae83c01b1249a0728","tid":808572,"uid":123335,"like":7,"dislike":121,"score":-114,"quote":{"pid":"141138f2441d73de2115cfe31b59369b675dba17","tid":808572,"uid":89931,"like":501,"dislike":2,"score":499,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"你應該直接右轉去睇醫生 唔係上嚟問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"醫生都放晒工啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實呢個問題都唔係第一次 <br />\n我起碼試過 above 30次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"都未死得咁咪唔使睇醫生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果死咗見到閻王嘅<br />\n咪叫佢幫你查下死因囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e791300e9b26a705906c930306aad8cb1a51d6d2","tid":808572,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"神。氣。精"},{"pid":"96f19ae3bb93e27b62613c0fdec4d28506ac2c16","tid":808572,"uid":43304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"中風先兆 or 小中風(微絲血管爆)<br />\n<br />\n中風未必關咖啡事, 一般建議避免少咖啡因<br />\n以免高血壓有危險<br />\n<br />\n早啲去急症check 清楚<br />\n你呢啲癥狀再講明自己懷疑中風<br />\n唔洗排好耐隊"},{"pid":"2f7e2d09350f02e8b2f7747537c7784bebdda045","tid":808572,"uid":203707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"Ching next life be careful"},{"pid":"66ff4370f71594f1bf4993a1afb4ddc9eddffdd8","tid":808572,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"樓主應該腦血管啲通道本身有少少問題<br />\n所以先會有咁樣既情況<br />\n<br />\n但調返轉, 你應該要多謝杯咖啡幫你誘發左呢啲情況出黎<br />\n等你可以預早知道<br />\n否則你應該會係等到某一日食食下飯暈低<br />\n起返身入左醫院半身郁唔到<br />\n<br />\nbtw 樓主可唔可以聯絡我<br />\n有啲野想問下你<br />\ntg <a href=\"https://t.me/Nightd1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FNightd1&d=%2FkFLIGE7jG3W9RG5LudnmU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7c73db75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Nightd1</a>"},{"pid":"551e22320499c4cc4d9134eedae0b76b92ca0c87","tid":808572,"uid":8786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"然後我上連登開個post, 屌，個腦又突然沉一沉，Loop 多次「爆腦」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedabcada29ee49d8925ff344875b6cf597703ba","tid":808572,"uid":65275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"爆seed姐 冇事嘅"},{"pid":"4076f0b3b8f12a176264564eb9c32d8eea913761","tid":808572,"uid":2655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"一飲咖啡個腦就沉一沉點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好飲咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15f9ad1e97f6013ea119b8f9b9d4e544873319a","tid":808572,"uid":174826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"之前都試下跑跑下步 突然眼前一黑左幾秒 同勁暈<br />\n坐低抖左陣先好返小小 但睇野都有D模 過多半個鐘左右就無咩野<br />\n果次真係嚇撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f65b9d77dc52a9d016621834531791e41a61e2","tid":808572,"uid":64155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c02067d87b5cf6caa03e0497a55732e97bffc668","tid":808572,"uid":105911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"樓主rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e519962ed16d726769c74693203e0e58ab706a8","tid":808572,"uid":64155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4